title.rendered: Windsor Brokers Celebrates Success at 2023 New Year Gala Dinner

content.rendered:
Windsor Brokers Celebrates Success at 2023 New Year Gala Dinner

Windsor Brokers was thrilled to host its annual gala party at the prestigious Aphrodite Hills resort on January 21, 2023. The evening was a delightful celebration of the past year’s hard work and a chance for our international teams to come together.

Guests were treated to a night of delicious food, great music, and excellent company. It was the perfect chance for everyone to let their hair down and enjoy some well-deserved relaxation after a busy year.

CEO Johny Abuaitah also made a heartwarming speech highlighting the major success stories throughout 2022 and touching light on his vision to move forward in 2023.

We would like to extend a big thank you to all our employees, partners, and clients who joined us for this special event. Your support and contributions have been instrumental in making Windsor Brokers the success it is today.

We look forward to many more years of celebration and success together. Here’s to marking a new chapter for Windsor Brokers, and many more to come.
